  "text": "# MORTGAGES  \n**Q: Does FirstUK Bank offer mortgages?**\nA: Yes. We offer residential mortgages with fixed rates (2 and 5-year terms) or variable rates.  \n**Q: What are current rates?**\nA:\n- Fixed 2-year: 4.50%–5.25% (depends on LTV)\n- Fixed 5-year: 5.00%–5.75% (depends on LTV)\n- Variable: BoE Base + 1.50%–2.25%  \n**Q: How much can I borrow?**\nA: Up to £500,000 for residential property.  \n**Q: How long is the loan term?**\nA: 2–25 years (you choose).  \n**Q: What's the application process?**\nA:\n1. Request mortgage information\n2. Submit application + documents\n3. Property valuation\n4. Underwriting review (5–10 days)\n5. Offer issued\n6. Legal completion\n7. Funds released  \n**Q: How long does the process take?**\nA: Typically 4–6 weeks from application to completion.  \n---",
